articles.title: Remco Evenepoel out of Giro d'Italia following COVID-19 positive - Cyclingnews
articles.description: Race leader withdraws 'with a heavy heart' after stage 9 time trial
articles.content:
Giro d'Italia leader Remco Evenepoel is out of the race on Sunday evening following a positive COVID-19 test, his Soudal-QuickStep team has announced.
